name: Tropical Giraffe | 500ml
description:
24 HOURS COLD 
Ice-cold drinks for up to 24 hours, regardless of the outside temperature. Our advanced double-walled vacuum insulation makes warm water a thing of the past.  
 
12 HOURS HOT 
Keep your tea or coffee hot for up to 12 hours. Perfect for those winter walks and cold morning commutes. Careful - Chilly's works a little too well!  
 
LEAK PROOF, SWEAT FREE 
Our airtight screw top lid prevents soaked bags and accidental spills. The vacuum insulation means your Chilly's Bottle will remain condensation free.  
 
QUALITY MATERIALS, BPA FREE 
Chilly's Bottles are constructed from durable, high-grade 304 stainless steel, for both the inside and outside walls. This preserves the flavour and freshness of your drink, without any tainting.
short_description: All Chilly's packaging is designed to compliment your Chilly's Bottle, making it the perfect gift. It is also made from recycled material, and is recyclable.

name: OPRO Silver Self-fit Mouthguard | Black/Red
description:
The durable outer layer of the dual layer Match Level Silver Self-Fit mouthguard from OPRO provides enhanced impact protection.
Unique features of the Silver mouthguard include:
  • Patented Fins provide a highly retentive fit after moulding
  • Drainage holes ensure the mouthguard doesn’t retain heat during the moulding process
  • Fitting Handle for ease of fitting
  • Biomaster Antimicrobial Protection proven to inhibit the growth of bacteria by up to 99.99%
  • Suitable for all contact sports
    The mouthguard’s stretch zones allow it to fit almost any mouth and the wide open palate makes speech and breathing easy whilst the mouthguard is being worn.
    The easy to fit mouthguard has 9 fins which break down on moulding to provide a superior custom-fit inner channel
  • Specially designed case
  • Latex Free
  • Not suitable for wearers of fixed braces
short_description:
Please click here for  How To Fit Guide

 

Silver-Adult
  • Suitable for up to age 10+

  • Suitable for up to age 10

name: Repton Pro Swim Suit | Rapids
description:
This fabric has been specifically developed for use in countries with high temperature & humidity. As a high stretch fabric, it is suitable for tailored or tight fitting garments. Using our Performex™ moisture management system it channels moisture away from the body, rapidly evaporating the moisture on the outside of the fabric, which, in turn, stops the body from overheating.

Washing Instructions

  • DO NOT TUMBLE DRY
  • Wash at 40c or below
  • Always look for the garment care label and follow the washing instructions
  • Garments of similar colours can be wash together where stated on the label
  • Wash match play garments promptly. Do not allow mud or stains to set

name: Repton Pro Swim Suit | Rapids
description:
This fabric has been specifically developed for use in countries with high temperature & humidity. As a high stretch fabric, it is suitable for tailored or tight fitting garments. Using our Performex™ moisture management system it channels moisture away from the body, rapidly evaporating the moisture on the outside of the fabric, which, in turn, stops the body from overheating.

Washing Instructions

  • DO NOT TUMBLE DRY
  • Wash at 40c or below
  • Always look for the garment care label and follow the washing instructions
  • Garments of similar colours can be wash together where stated on the label
  • Wash match play garments promptly. Do not allow mud or stains to set

Features a soft, cotton lined hood,Ribbed cuffs and hem,Kangaroo pocket for snug comfort. Traditional Hoodie fabric, available in an excellent quality & wright. It offers a high level of warmth to the wearer

Washing Instructions

  • DO NOT TUMBLE DRY
  • Wash at 40c or below
  • Always look for the garment care label and follow the washing instructions
  • Garments of similar colours can be wash together where stated on the label
  • Wash match play garments promptly. Do not allow mud or stains to set

name: Rash Vest | Boys
description:
This fabric has been specifically developed for use in countries with high temperature & humidity. As a high stretch fabric, it is suitable for tailored or tight fitting garments. Using our Performex™ moisture management system it channels moisture away from the body, rapidly evaporating the moisture on the outside of the fabric, which, in turn, stops the body from overheating.

Washing Instructions

  • DO NOT TUMBLE DRY
  • Wash at 40c or below
  • Always look for the garment care label and follow the washing instructions
  • Garments of similar colours can be wash together where stated on the label
  • Wash match play garments promptly. Do not allow mud or stains to set
short_description:
Please click here for  Size Guide

name: All in One Swimsuit
description:
This fabric has been specifically developed for use in countries with high temperature & humidity. As a high stretch fabric, it is suitable for tailored or tight fitting garments. Using our Performex™ moisture management system it channels moisture away from the body, rapidly evaporating the moisture on the outside of the fabric, which, in turn, stops the body from overheating.

Washing Instructions

  • DO NOT TUMBLE DRY
  • Wash at 40c or below
  • Always look for the garment care label and follow the washing instructions
  • Garments of similar colours can be wash together where stated on the label
  • Wash match play garments promptly. Do not allow mud or stains to set

This fabric has been specifically developed for use in countries with high temperature & humidity. As a high stretch fabric, it is suitable for tailored or tight fitting garments. Using our Performex™ moisture management system it channels moisture away from the body, rapidly evaporating the moisture on the outside of the fabric, which, in turn, stops the body from overheating.

Washing Instructions

  • DO NOT TUMBLE DRY
  • Wash at 40c or below
  • Always look for the garment care label and follow the washing instructions
  • Garments of similar colours can be wash together where stated on the label
  • Wash match play garments promptly. Do not allow mud or stains to set

name: DIA Swimming Jammer
description:
This fabric has been specifically developed for use in countries with high temperature & humidity. As a high stretch fabric, it is suitable for tailored or tight fitting garments. Using our Performex™ moisture management system it channels moisture away from the body, rapidly evaporating the moisture on the outside of the fabric, which, in turn, stops the body from overheating.

Washing Instructions

  • DO NOT TUMBLE DRY
  • Wash at 40c or below
  • Always look for the garment care label and follow the washing instructions
  • Garments of similar colours can be wash together where stated on the label
  • Wash match play garments promptly. Do not allow mud or stains to set
